Phase III of the Hailan Bay? Why are you alone?

45
00:05:33,379 --> 00:05:40,512
Someone else will come soon,
but I need to talk to you in private first.

46
00:05:40,512 --> 00:05:43,200
What is it?

47
00:05:43,499 --> 00:05:47,339
Jin Yu. I like you.

48
00:05:47,339 --> 00:05:52,379
