54
00:06:16,448 --> 00:06:20,579
I understand. After we get married,
I won't interfere with your freedom.

55
00:06:20,579 --> 00:06:24,379
I'll be a good and obedient wife
as long as you stay with me.

56
00:06:24,379 --> 00:06:28,640
