60
00:06:49,779 --> 00:06:56,259
It's Ye Meng. The other day,
she showed me and Ms. Li around Ningsui.

61
00:06:56,259 --> 00:07:03,432
Mr. Ye, this is Li Jin Yu.
He is in charge of the project.

62
00:07:03,456 --> 00:07:05,179
Hello.

63
00:07:05,179 --> 00:07:09,579
Sorry, I need to use the restroom.

64
00:07:17,339 --> 00:07:23,139
Lin Yang Yang. you're smarter than I imagined.

65
00:07:23,459 --> 00:07:26,496
